quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  74,32,"Daabi, Mede bosome"
  74,33,"Ne anadwo, εberε a εbεdane neho (akͻ)"
  74,34,"Ne Anͻpa, εberε a animu bεteteε no di nse sε"
  74,35,"Nokorε, (Amanehunu gya no) yε (mmusuo) akεseε no mu baako"
  74,36,Ɛyε kͻkͻbͻ dema adasamma
  74,37,(Ɛyε kͻkͻbͻ) dema momu obi a ͻpεsε onya nkͻsoͻ anaasε ͻka akyire
  74,38,Yε’de onipa biara kraa asi awowa ama (ͻno ara) n’adwuma a odiiε
  74,39,Mmom nifa so foͻ no deε
  74,40,Wͻn wͻ Aheman mu rebisa
  74,41,Abͻneεfoͻ no sε
  74,42,“Ɛdeεn na εde mo kͻͻ Amane hunu gya no mu?”
  74,43,"Wͻ’bεka sε: ”Na yεnnka wͻn a wͻ’frε Nyame no ho"
  74,44,"Afei na yεnnka wͻn a, wͻ’ma ahiafoͻ biribi die no ho"
  74,45,Na yεka ahohwifoͻ no ho ne wͻn ka nsεm hunu
  74,46,Na yεnnnye Atemmuda no nni
  74,47,"Kͻpem sε, (owuo a) εda biribiara adi pefee no bεtoo yεn.’’"
  74,48,"Enti (saa nkorͻfoͻ no), otwitwagyeni biara ntwitwagyeε ho mma mfasoͻ mma wͻn"
  74,49,"Na deεn na εha wͻn a, enti wͻ’retwe wͻn ho afiri Afutusεm no ho a"
  74,50,"W’ayε (wͻn ho) sε mfunumuu a, wabͻhu"
  74,51,a wᴐ’redwane gyata
  74,52,"Daabi, wͻn mu nipa biara pεsε yεnto nkrataa (a, obiara din wͻ nedeε soͻ) nhwete ma no"
  74,53,"Hwε, Daabi da, (saa nkorͻfoͻ no) nnsuro Daakye (Atemmuda) no"
  74,54,"Daabi, Qur’aan yε Afutusεm"
  74,55,Enti obi a ͻpε no ͻnfa ntu ne ho fo
  74,56,"Nanso wͻ’nnfa nntu wͻn ho fo, gyesε Nyankopͻn pε; Ɔno ne Obi a εsεsε yesuro no, na yε’yε Neho ahwεyie, na Ɔno ne Obi a Ɔde bͻne kyε"